title: Ep 15: Moving Out and Moving On
itunes:title: Ep 15: Moving Out and Moving On
description: WELP. The last 3 months have been a doozy, but WE BACK BABY. Shannon fills you in on everything that’s happened in the time away, her move to New York, her unexpected move in Nashville, and who the hell is Wifi guy? She’ll answer your burning questions about her ex moving on and feature a new segment called “Ask Shannon”. Auntie Shan gives some advice on texting, her outlook on confidence in life and how does one cut down a roster? All of this and much more in Season 2 Episode 1!
